*hamster-applet-2.30.2 (22 Jun 2010)

  22 Jun 2010; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> -hamster-applet-2.30.1.ebuild,
  +hamster-applet-2.30.2.ebuild:
  Version bump: avoid draining laptop's battery, minor bugfixes that improve
  the overall usability of the app, updated translations. Remove old
  testing.

  15 Jun 2010; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> hamster-applet-2.30.1.ebuild:
  Add RDEPEND on dev-python/pyxdg as reported by Frank in bug 324143.

